1
-1:59:57,500 --> 00:00:01,500
<i>Secret</i>

2
00:00:15,800 --> 00:00:18,360
<i> I don't remember the way home.</i>

3
00:00:18,360 --> 00:00:19,910
<i> Now take me to Yoo Jeong.</i>

4
00:00:19,910 --> 00:00:23,350
<i> Yoo Jeong is waiting. </i>

5
00:00:24,300 --> 00:00:26,490
<i> Did you remember that?</i>

6
00:00:26,530 --> 00:00:30,460
<i> Why shouldn't I? You're the one who drove.</i>

7
00:00:30,460 --> 00:00:34,100
<i> You're blaming it on Yoo Jeong. Do you think I wouldn't know that?</i>

8
00:01:08,870 --> 00:01:10,600
Substitute.

9
00:01:20,300 --> 00:01:21,740
Kang Yoo Jeong.

10
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:31,940
Substitute!

11
00:01:45,150 --> 00:01:51,930
<i>♫ Would it be alright if I move closer</i>

12
00:01:51,930 --> 00:01:56,030
<i>♫ I was scared so I stood still</i>

13
00:01:56,030 --> 00:01:57,560
Driver.

14
00:01:58,700 --> 00:02:04,610
<i>♫ I wonder if we really had to meet</i>

15
00:02:07,580 --> 00:02:09,770
What are you doing?

16
00:02:10,700 --> 00:02:18,150
<i>♫ Because an unerasable scar hurts</i>

17
00:02:18,150 --> 00:02:24,850
<i>♫ Would I be able to tell you again that 
I love you</i>

18
00:02:24,850 --> 00:02:31,640
<i>♫ No matter how many times I let you go, 
you're still the one</i>

19
00:02:31,640 --> 00:02:38,550
<i>♫ No matter how hard I try to erase you, 
like an incurable disease</i>

20
00:02:38,550 --> 00:02:42,240
<i>♫ Spreading inside of me</i>

21
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:49,230
<i>♫ I just can't stop this love</i>

22
00:03:13,960 --> 00:03:15,850
Why are you here at this time?

23
00:03:31,260 --> 00:03:33,600
What happened, Do Hoon?

24
00:03:35,070 --> 00:03:36,640
I'll make you some tea.

25
00:03:36,640 --> 00:03:38,350
Wait.

26
00:03:44,500 --> 00:03:46,420
Please just stay like this for a second.

27
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:25,070
<i>Secret Episode 11</i>

28
00:04:52,850 --> 00:04:54,480
I'm sorry.

29
00:05:41,400 --> 00:05:43,400
You always...

30
00:05:44,340 --> 00:05:46,810
come inside my building and cry.

31
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:49,130
I'm sorry.

32
00:05:49,130 --> 00:05:51,100
What is it this time?

33
00:05:58,870 --> 00:06:00,900
Towards you...

34
00:06:02,610 --> 00:06:04,730
I am sorry.

35
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:09,310
To see loved ones pass...

36
00:06:10,570 --> 00:06:14,600
I know it doesn't happen only to me...

37
00:06:16,130 --> 00:06:18,560
Because my dad,

38
00:06:18,560 --> 00:06:21,440
my San, I sent them away like that...

39
00:06:23,300 --> 00:06:27,270
and I feel so shameless being alive by myself.

40
00:06:29,530 --> 00:06:31,900
So how disgusting would I

41
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:35,270
be to you?

42
00:06:37,470 --> 00:06:39,770
That's fine if you know.

43
00:06:42,260 --> 00:06:44,400
That helped me, too.

44
00:06:46,320 --> 00:06:50,020
I'm not brave enough to die along side Ji Hee

45
00:06:52,210 --> 00:06:54,770
but I found you

46
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:58,850
and hated you to death

47
00:06:59,590 --> 00:07:01,770
to withstand it all.

48
00:07:10,310 --> 00:07:11,930
You should

49
00:07:15,850 --> 00:07:18,190
withstand it while watching me.

50
00:07:49,430 --> 00:07:52,400
What's making it so difficult for you, Do Hoon?

51
00:07:54,450 --> 00:07:56,310
People.

52
00:07:59,650 --> 00:08:02,730
I became a prosecutor through another's sacrifice.

53
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:07,150
I came up here without anything in my hand.

54
00:08:07,900 --> 00:08:09,350
But...

55
00:08:10,490 --> 00:08:13,520
people on top are always predetermined.

56
00:08:15,860 --> 00:08:18,350
I gave up everything and came up here,

57
00:08:18,830 --> 00:08:21,690
but those who sacrificed are in my way.

58
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:25,610
Those who are up here aren't any different.

59
00:08:25,610 --> 00:08:27,950
You would think it's luxury,

60
00:08:27,990 --> 00:08:32,470
but I give up a lot, too, trying to live up to my parents' expectations. If you know that...

61
00:08:32,470 --> 00:08:34,320
I know.

62
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:36,350
We both gave up, but

63
00:08:37,130 --> 00:08:39,440
we began with different things in our hands.

64
00:08:40,240 --> 00:08:42,320
Since when was the world fair?

65
00:08:42,360 --> 00:08:44,310
It isn't fair.

66
00:08:44,630 --> 00:08:49,650
But if you end it just complaining about it, you're the one that is foolish.

67
00:08:51,460 --> 00:08:52,770
Thank you

68
00:08:54,130 --> 00:08:55,560
for your advice.

69
00:08:56,280 --> 00:08:57,980
It's not advice.

70
00:08:58,650 --> 00:09:01,600
I'm just encouraging you to not give up.

71
00:09:10,050 --> 00:09:14,600
Hi.

72
00:09:17,290 --> 00:09:20,170
It's time to go check restaurant #43.

73
00:09:20,170 --> 00:09:21,480
I know.

74
00:09:23,180 --> 00:09:24,950
Gwang Soo,

75
00:09:24,950 --> 00:09:27,060
how do you think she is doing right now?

76
00:09:27,810 --> 00:09:29,440
How...?

77
00:09:31,530 --> 00:09:32,930
Is there something wrong?

78
00:09:32,930 --> 00:09:34,730
No, it's fine.

79
00:09:35,400 --> 00:09:36,940
Let's go.

80
00:09:37,640 --> 00:09:41,030
You can't see me relax on my one day off...

81
00:09:41,070 --> 00:09:43,150
Please, Hye Ri, just for today.

82
00:09:43,150 --> 00:09:46,920
I will take your place next time whenever you want to take off.

83
00:09:46,920 --> 00:09:49,820
Anyway, is there something wrong? What's wrong with your face?

84
00:09:49,820 --> 00:09:52,200
You didn't even come home last night.

85
00:09:52,900 --> 00:09:54,310
Forget it.

86
00:09:54,850 --> 00:09:56,500
I'm going.

87
00:09:56,500 --> 00:09:58,480
Thank you.

88
00:10:21,640 --> 00:10:23,600
Turn the car around to Hapjoong-dong.

89
00:10:23,600 --> 00:10:25,290
I'm worried about Kang Yoo Jeong

90
00:10:25,290 --> 00:10:27,370
Did something happen?

91
00:10:27,370 --> 00:10:29,440
She acts like nothing happened.

92
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:31,330
That's why it's weird.

93
00:10:33,320 --> 00:10:35,130
I...

94
00:10:35,180 --> 00:10:37,960
saw someone like that before...

95
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:40,810
Anyway, I'm worried, so turn the car around and go back.

96
00:10:40,810 --> 00:10:42,160
Okay.

97
00:11:01,570 --> 00:11:03,390
Manager. Yes, Boss.

98
00:11:03,390 --> 00:11:04,700
Hello.

99
00:11:05,190 --> 00:11:07,880
I don't see Kang Yoo Jeong.

100
00:11:07,880 --> 00:11:11,380
She said she has some emergency, so she switched shifts with Hye Ri.

101
00:11:17,700 --> 00:11:18,940
Where is Kang Yoo Jeong?

102
00:11:18,940 --> 00:11:21,480
Ahh...that...I'm not very sure.

103
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:23,040
You don't know? Does that make sense?

104
00:11:23,040 --> 00:11:26,300
I asked but she didn't reply.

105
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:28,820
She only asked me to switch shifts.

106
00:11:43,100 --> 00:11:45,970
It's written here. This is our phone number.

107
00:11:46,010 --> 00:11:48,790
When the patient is missing, they contact us

108
00:11:48,790 --> 00:11:50,630
from where he was first missing.

109
00:11:50,630 --> 00:11:54,600
My father had this bracelet, too.

110
00:11:54,600 --> 00:11:56,530
But...

111
00:11:56,530 --> 00:11:58,360
it was missing...

112
00:11:58,400 --> 00:12:00,350
You can't take this off by yourself.

113
00:12:00,350 --> 00:12:02,440
Look at this.

114
00:12:03,560 --> 00:12:07,030
By any chance, can you check whether there was a call?

115
00:12:07,030 --> 00:12:10,190
If there was, we would have contacted you already.

116
00:12:10,760 --> 00:12:14,330
The guardian is Ahn Do Hoon, right?

117
00:12:27,970 --> 00:12:29,790
You can go first.

118
00:12:33,020 --> 00:12:35,400
What's up?

119
00:12:35,400 --> 00:12:36,710
I don't have a reason to see you.

120
00:12:36,710 --> 00:12:38,140
I have.

121
00:12:38,140 --> 00:12:39,580
Let's go out.

122
00:12:44,230 --> 00:12:46,640
I don't have time. I have to attend the meeting.

123
00:12:48,220 --> 00:12:49,650
This is more important than the meeting.

124
00:12:49,650 --> 00:12:51,190
Go out!

125
00:12:55,090 --> 00:12:57,350
Director, are you ok?

126
00:12:57,350 --> 00:12:58,430
I said I have something to say.

127
00:12:58,430 --> 00:12:59,240
Take her out.

128
00:12:59,240 --> 00:12:59,860
Oppa.

129
00:12:59,860 --> 00:13:01,300
Hurry!

130
00:13:01,300 --> 00:13:03,340
Oppa! Oppa!

131
00:13:03,360 --> 00:13:06,410
Oppa!

132
00:13:06,940 --> 00:13:11,710
Oppa!

133
00:13:12,250 --> 00:13:15,870
Oppa!

134
00:13:16,390 --> 00:13:17,990
Oppa!

135
00:13:23,820 --> 00:13:26,490
I said she's not here! Why don't you believe me?!

136
00:13:26,490 --> 00:13:27,540
So where is she?

137
00:13:27,540 --> 00:13:28,920
I wanted to ask you the same thing.

138
00:13:28,920 --> 00:13:32,180
She went to work but why hasn't been back for 2 days?

139
00:13:34,150 --> 00:13:36,270
What happened to Kang Yoo Jeong?

140
00:13:36,270 --> 00:13:39,020
You know where she is.

141
00:13:39,080 --> 00:13:41,070
Maybe she hid somewhere because something happened.

142
00:13:41,110 --> 00:13:44,980
She has so many things going on already, 
can't you just leave her alone?

143
00:14:50,640 --> 00:14:52,840
What do you think you're doing?

144
00:14:53,420 --> 00:14:56,760
When I went to Pohang to find my dad...

145
00:14:56,760 --> 00:14:59,080
his bracelet was missing.

146
00:14:59,810 --> 00:15:02,350
The bracelet...

147
00:15:02,970 --> 00:15:06,190
Didn't you say it's not something that can be taken off by yourself?

148
00:15:06,190 --> 00:15:08,400
Why are you asking me this?

149
00:15:09,630 --> 00:15:11,440
Because that day...

150
00:15:11,440 --> 00:15:14,830
you saw my dad.

151
00:15:15,610 --> 00:15:16,680
No?

152
00:15:16,680 --> 00:15:18,460
Yes, I saw him.

153
00:15:19,980 --> 00:15:21,860
He got in the car.

154
00:15:21,860 --> 00:15:24,060
But he kept trying to get out.

155
00:15:25,070 --> 00:15:28,790
I stopped the car on the shoulder to avoid an accident,

156
00:15:28,790 --> 00:15:31,330
but he just ran out of the car.

157
00:15:32,320 --> 00:15:33,580
Lies.

158
00:15:33,580 --> 00:15:36,110
It was raining and there were a lot of people so I couldn't find him.

159
00:15:36,110 --> 00:15:39,780
So, you want to blame me?

160
00:15:39,780 --> 00:15:40,870
Lies.

161
00:15:40,890 --> 00:15:42,580
So what if I'm lying?

162
00:15:42,580 --> 00:15:46,560
Yes, so what if I threw out your dad? So what?!

163
00:15:48,620 --> 00:15:51,430
The one who couldn't take care of your dad is you.

164
00:15:52,050 --> 00:15:55,020
You're the one who didn't agree to send him to a nursing home!

165
00:15:55,040 --> 00:15:58,410
It was for your greed and your satisfaction!

166
00:15:59,870 --> 00:16:02,090
My dad...

167
00:16:04,520 --> 00:16:06,190
He trusted you.

168
00:16:06,190 --> 00:16:09,920
Yes. Yes, and I'm sick of that.

169
00:16:09,920 --> 00:16:14,600
So? So what if I didn't go after him? So what?!

170
00:16:18,810 --> 00:16:20,610
Stop the car.

171
00:16:24,440 --> 00:16:26,160
Stop the car.

172
00:16:26,790 --> 00:16:28,730
Stop it!

173
00:16:30,060 --> 00:16:32,600
I said stop the car!

174
00:16:58,460 --> 00:16:59,760
Are you crazy?

175
00:16:59,760 --> 00:17:01,890
What if an accident happened?!

176
00:17:02,760 --> 00:17:05,090
Why did you do it?

177
00:17:06,800 --> 00:17:12,280
How could you do that to me?

178
00:17:12,280 --> 00:17:14,640
To my dad?!

179
00:17:24,800 --> 00:17:27,520
Because you were sick of it,

180
00:17:28,130 --> 00:17:30,960
is that why you took San away, too?

181
00:17:33,680 --> 00:17:36,200
Is that why you took him away...

182
00:17:36,200 --> 00:17:38,370
and left him to die?

183
00:17:38,370 --> 00:17:40,800
What are you talking about?

184
00:17:41,360 --> 00:17:43,710
You really did go crazy.

185
00:17:54,150 --> 00:17:57,130
Get out.

186
00:18:01,490 --> 00:18:04,530
How can I not go crazy?

187
00:18:05,660 --> 00:18:09,000
How could you act so normal, Oppa?

188
00:18:11,670 --> 00:18:14,190
Kneel down!

189
00:18:14,190 --> 00:18:16,310
To San...

190
00:18:16,310 --> 00:18:18,470
To my dad, apologize to them!

191
00:18:18,510 --> 00:18:20,850
Kneel down and beg!

192
00:18:22,940 --> 00:18:24,890
If I kneel down...

193
00:18:24,890 --> 00:18:27,560
If I apologize...

194
00:18:27,560 --> 00:18:29,960
Will you disappear?

195
00:18:36,450 --> 00:18:39,180
I don't want to live looking back anymore.

196
00:18:39,850 --> 00:18:43,060
You're there at the end, in the back.

197
00:18:43,060 --> 00:18:45,570
You're holding on to me, it's disgusting!

198
00:18:46,600 --> 00:18:48,880
Disgusting?

199
00:18:49,410 --> 00:18:50,680
Me?

200
00:18:50,680 --> 00:18:53,580
I was arrogant when I said

201
00:18:54,040 --> 00:18:56,570
I could make you happy.

202
00:18:56,570 --> 00:18:59,190
You said you don't regret it?

203
00:18:59,190 --> 00:19:01,950
I regret it!!!

204
00:19:01,970 --> 00:19:04,160
That day!

205
00:19:04,210 --> 00:19:07,510
The day when you said you would go in place of me.

206
00:19:07,510 --> 00:19:10,150
If I had left you then,

207
00:19:10,150 --> 00:19:13,300
I wouldn't be regretting it now.

208
00:19:19,460 --> 00:19:22,000
Regrets...

209
00:19:22,060 --> 00:19:24,860
you will start from this moment.

210
00:19:25,770 --> 00:19:28,610
Till you rip your heart out with regret,

211
00:19:28,610 --> 00:19:31,450
and I will make it happen.

212
00:19:32,220 --> 00:19:34,690
Watch it carefully!

213
00:19:35,440 --> 00:19:38,040
So that you never forget me,

214
00:19:38,040 --> 00:19:40,520
my San,

215
00:19:41,660 --> 00:19:44,800
my father who thought of you as his own son!

216
00:19:44,830 --> 00:19:47,380
I'll make it so that you can never forget!

217
00:19:49,160 --> 00:19:52,080
Disappear from you?

218
00:19:52,650 --> 00:19:55,550
Don't even dream about it.

219
00:19:55,610 --> 00:19:58,760
Wherever you go, I will be there.

220
00:19:58,770 --> 00:20:01,880
You will see me until you're sick to death!

221
00:20:03,160 --> 00:20:05,540
Don't think about running away.

222
00:22:03,680 --> 00:22:05,670
Why did you come?

223
00:22:06,400 --> 00:22:13,100
I would like to be... by your side, Boss.

224
00:22:15,800 --> 00:22:17,120
Why?

225
00:22:17,120 --> 00:22:19,020
Because I have something I should do.

226
00:22:20,750 --> 00:22:23,160
There is something I must do.

227
00:22:23,620 --> 00:22:25,540
Without even knowing the reason,

228
00:22:25,540 --> 00:22:27,330
did you think I would help you?

229
00:22:27,330 --> 00:22:29,610
As you want, President...

230
00:22:31,460 --> 00:22:34,030
I will not live a happy life.

231
00:22:35,900 --> 00:22:38,150
The most miserable life possible,

232
00:22:39,770 --> 00:22:41,840
I'll live like that for you.

233
00:22:43,020 --> 00:22:45,160
I am asking you.

234
00:22:47,610 --> 00:22:49,660
Why should I help you?

235
00:22:50,790 --> 00:22:53,190
Is it because of Ahn Do Hoon?

236
00:23:00,720 --> 00:23:02,440
What is this?

237
00:23:03,790 --> 00:23:07,370
What about the time when you protected him, 
as if you would die in his place,

238
00:23:07,370 --> 00:23:09,260
suddenly why?

239
00:23:10,870 --> 00:23:14,120
What I can do for those people I lost,

240
00:23:15,510 --> 00:23:17,870
because this is the only way.

241
00:23:18,720 --> 00:23:21,560
Even though I can't get back 
what was taken away from me,

242
00:23:22,720 --> 00:23:24,730
I have something I must receive.

243
00:23:32,510 --> 00:23:36,190
<i>Director Ahn Do Hoon</i>

244
00:23:44,800 --> 00:23:47,740
I will make it so that...

245
00:23:47,780 --> 00:23:50,930
Your heart is torn with regret.

246
00:23:50,930 --> 00:23:53,380
<i>Watch carefully.</i>

247
00:23:53,420 --> 00:23:55,400
<i>So that you can't erase me</i>

248
00:23:55,400 --> 00:23:59,330
<i> my son San, and my dad who thought of you like a son.</i>

249
00:23:59,330 --> 00:24:01,400
<i>I'll make it so you can never forget.</i>

250
00:24:01,400 --> 00:24:03,430
<i>This time too</i>

251
00:24:03,430 --> 00:24:06,000
<i>If you do that again, I won't let it slide.</i>

252
00:24:06,000 --> 00:24:08,540
<i>Okay, Son-in law?</i>

253
00:24:12,070 --> 00:24:14,360
<i>Wherever you go, I'll be there.</i>

254
00:24:15,210 --> 00:24:17,910
<i>So you'll disgustingly see me!</i>

255
00:24:22,880 --> 00:24:24,440
I will not regret.

256
00:24:25,030 --> 00:24:26,770
I will not

257
00:24:26,770 --> 00:24:28,910
look back anymore.

258
00:24:29,580 --> 00:24:30,910
Yoo Jeong.

259
00:24:38,730 --> 00:24:40,850
Ahn Do Hoon crumbling

260
00:24:40,850 --> 00:24:42,960
is something I've wanted as well.

261
00:24:43,330 --> 00:24:47,200
Why bother choosing a difficult way?

262
00:24:48,030 --> 00:24:51,550
Wouldn't kicking him out of K Group solve the problem?

263
00:24:52,000 --> 00:24:54,050
Were you

264
00:24:55,270 --> 00:24:57,730
satisfied

265
00:24:58,500 --> 00:25:00,950
because you took it all away from me, Deputy Head?

266
00:25:03,680 --> 00:25:06,870
If you take things away so easily,

267
00:25:06,870 --> 00:25:09,640
you won't comprehend how precious the things

268
00:25:10,210 --> 00:25:12,910
you've taken away are.

269
00:25:12,910 --> 00:25:14,130
Then,

270
00:25:15,220 --> 00:25:17,420
what is the reason you need me?

271
00:25:21,930 --> 00:25:23,780
Because you...

272
00:25:24,660 --> 00:25:27,460
you make Do Hoon Oppa more tenacious.

273
00:25:31,740 --> 00:25:34,430
That way I'll not weaken.

