00:25:34,430 --> 00:25:38,300
"Give me one more chance." "Think of our past."

275
00:25:38,340 --> 00:25:40,830
So that I'll not be shaken by such words.

276
00:26:06,930 --> 00:26:08,680
Ahn Do Hoon,

277
00:26:10,540 --> 00:26:13,400
