278
00:26:16,000 --> 00:26:17,550
Gwang Soo...

279
00:26:18,490 --> 00:26:20,730
Use whatever method necessary

280
00:26:21,100 --> 00:26:24,630
to find out what Kang Yoo Jeong did and who she met with

281
00:26:24,630 --> 00:26:26,600
for the past week.

282
00:26:27,170 --> 00:26:28,610
Unni.

283
00:26:35,690 --> 00:26:37,330
Is there anything to eat?

284
00:26:38,270 --> 00:26:41,160
You come home for the first time in 2 days, and
all you can say is "Rice"?

285
00:26:41,200 --> 00:26:43,180
Whatever happened, you should say something!

286
00:26:43,180 --> 00:26:45,140
I'm hungry.

287
00:26:45,140 --> 00:26:47,480
I think I need to eat a bit.

288
00:26:48,040 --> 00:26:51,100
I need energy to work, don't I?

289
00:26:52,450 --> 00:26:54,730
I made some yellow bean stew.

290
00:26:56,720 --> 00:26:58,320
Follow me...

291
00:27:11,080 --> 00:27:13,060
Until the end of the second half this year,

292
00:27:13,090 --> 00:27:16,560
we plan on completing the projects for 
in-country and overseas hotels.

293
00:27:16,590 --> 00:27:20,810
During the slow season, hotel bidding system, 
the first in Korea...

294
00:27:22,780 --> 00:27:25,140
I get the data, too.

295
00:27:25,140 --> 00:27:27,640
Then what did you call me
all the way over here for?

296
00:27:27,640 --> 00:27:29,470
It seems you're curious.

297
00:27:32,970 --> 00:27:36,020
Since I'm not good at twisting the words around,

298
00:27:36,940 --> 00:27:39,390
What happened between you and Kang Yoo Jeong?

299
00:27:40,990 --> 00:27:45,310
What did you do and how, 
for Kang Yoo Jeong to turn around like that?

300
00:27:46,240 --> 00:27:50,020
If you have nothing work related to discuss, I'll be going.

301
00:27:50,020 --> 00:27:51,310
Lawyer Ahn.

302
00:27:53,740 --> 00:27:57,520
You too were there on the day of the accident.

303
00:27:58,100 --> 00:28:01,540
For the two of you who shares a secret like the life itself,

304
00:28:01,540 --> 00:28:05,660
why you both ended up being so against each other, 
I'm so curious, I'm about to go crazy.

305
00:28:07,320 --> 00:28:10,210
Neither of you are telling.

306
00:28:11,120 --> 00:28:12,780
Gwang Soo?

307
00:28:12,780 --> 00:28:13,980
Yes.

308
00:28:13,980 --> 00:28:15,940
Are you checking it out?

309
00:28:16,870 --> 00:28:20,280
The blackbox video will be restored soon.

310
00:28:20,280 --> 00:28:21,920
Okay.

311
00:28:24,880 --> 00:28:26,930
I'll see you at the Board Meeting.

312
00:28:33,290 --> 00:28:34,780
Oh,

313
00:28:35,250 --> 00:28:38,200
At the Board Meeting, Se Yeon is also coming, right?

314
00:28:38,700 --> 00:28:43,030
Does Se Yeon know about the relationship 
between you and Kang Yoo Jeong?

315
00:28:43,830 --> 00:28:47,030
My warning that you shouldn't be seeing Se Yeon,

316
00:28:47,740 --> 00:28:49,720
