317
00:29:27,320 --> 00:29:31,850
At King's Restaurant, the person who is assisting me with revenue growth and for new leaps,

318
00:29:31,850 --> 00:29:34,270
I would like to introduce to you my partner.

319
00:29:39,260 --> 00:29:41,290
I'm Kang Yoo Jeong.

320
00:29:55,790 --> 00:29:58,770
Since when, enough for you to be able to attend the meeting,

321
00:29:58,810 --> 00:30:00,920
were you promoted?

322
00:30:05,040 --> 00:30:10,300
The Boss isn't yet familiar with the restaurant's menu, 
so I came with him.

323
00:30:11,670 --> 00:30:13,860
Please don't misunderstand.

324
00:30:13,860 --> 00:30:16,120
You said that last time as well.

325
00:30:17,260 --> 00:30:18,900
But what to do?

326
00:30:19,710 --> 00:30:23,950
He keeps misunderstanding.

327
00:30:25,490 --> 00:30:29,540
What is the real reason you keep sticking to Min Hyeok?

328
00:30:39,100 --> 00:30:41,600
Please excuse me.

329
00:30:50,450 --> 00:30:52,520
Miss Kang Yoo Jeong, what you said to me...

330
00:30:52,530 --> 00:30:55,010
This is it?

331
00:30:55,010 --> 00:30:59,660
To use Jo Min Hyeok to get a promotion in your status?

332
00:30:59,660 --> 00:31:05,080
Mr Attorney, didn't you get up there like that, too?

333
00:31:13,200 --> 00:31:16,510
It isn't different from the reason you 
have Ahn Do Hoon by your side.

334
00:31:16,510 --> 00:31:18,650
I also need someone by my side.

335
00:31:18,650 --> 00:31:21,960
You really are going crazy.

336
00:31:22,960 --> 00:31:27,050
You even know what kind of woman she is.

337
00:31:27,050 --> 00:31:32,940
And if you knew what kind of man Lawyer Ahn was,
it would be different.

338
00:31:35,970 --> 00:31:38,150
Let's go, Substitute.

339
00:32:04,120 --> 00:32:06,380
Come to work at my house tomorrow.

340
00:32:07,340 --> 00:32:08,240
Again?

341
00:32:08,240 --> 00:32:10,720
I told you not to talk back to me.

342
00:32:12,170 --> 00:32:13,630
Yes.

343
00:32:18,600 --> 00:32:20,800
Is this much enough?

344
00:32:21,460 --> 00:32:23,640
In front of Ahn Do Hoon,

345
00:32:24,390 --> 00:32:26,650
be more confident.

346
00:32:26,700 --> 00:32:28,100
Yes.

347
00:32:31,700 --> 00:32:33,830
Thank you.

348
00:32:40,610 --> 00:32:44,680
What do those two think they are doing?

349
00:32:44,720 --> 00:32:47,540
At least those two together...

350
00:32:49,100 --> 00:32:53,000
succeeded in getting your attention Se Yeon.

351
00:32:53,000 --> 00:32:54,990
It bothers me.

352
00:32:56,240 --> 00:32:59,080
If you want, Se Yeon, I can

353
00:33:00,440 --> 00:33:02,430
split those two apart.

354
00:33:30,480 --> 00:33:32,230
What is this?

355
00:33:35,600 --> 00:33:39,100
<i>K Group Chairman Jo rumored in critical condition.
His secret departure to Germany revealed...</i>

356
00:33:39,100 --> 00:33:42,300
<i>K Group, K Construction's unreasonable building
leads to negative fund turnover ratio.</i>

357
00:33:43,900 --> 00:33:46,500
How do I stop the articles?

358
00:33:47,300 --> 00:33:48,800
What's this?

359
00:33:49,960 --> 00:33:54,190
These people all blab that they know everything,
so how come this is the first time I'm hearing about it?!

360
00:33:55,010 --> 00:33:56,900
When will Father return?

361
00:33:56,900 --> 00:34:01,100
Using Director Im and my name, we've planned to get
 a $20M credit loan from K Capital.

362
00:34:01,120 --> 00:34:02,750
First, we must stabilize the share price...

363
00:34:02,750 --> 00:34:04,870
What about Father? What does he say?

364
00:34:06,500 --> 00:34:08,500
Why did he go to Germany?

365
00:34:09,410 --> 00:34:10,600
Why did he go?!

366
00:34:10,600 --> 00:34:12,830
We can't let the Chairman know.

367
00:34:12,830 --> 00:34:16,320
We made it so no one can contact him during the surgery period.

368
00:34:16,320 --> 00:34:18,450
Surgery?

369
00:34:20,400 --> 00:34:23,180
What I don't even know as a son, 
the rumer sites are letting me know!

370
00:34:23,180 --> 00:34:26,400
While Chairman isn't here, the head of K Group is you!

371
00:34:26,400 --> 00:34:30,500
The person who knows that didn't think to TELL ME ANYTHING?!

372
00:34:38,820 --> 00:34:40,420
K Hotel...

373
00:34:41,800 --> 00:34:43,450
Start purchasing K Hotel shares first.

374
00:34:43,500 --> 00:34:45,320
It was father's first business.

375
00:34:46,360 --> 00:34:47,970
How's Father's condition?

376
00:34:48,010 --> 00:34:49,630
We'll get notified soon.

377
00:34:49,630 --> 00:34:51,530
You must return to the Hotel immediately.

378
00:34:51,550 --> 00:34:53,560
Prove that you lack nothing as the successor.

379
00:34:53,600 --> 00:34:55,200
Is this why Father said

380
00:34:55,200 --> 00:35:00,250
we must make the restaurant business successful?

381
00:35:00,250 --> 00:35:05,880
Chairman and K Group won't collapse that easily.

382
00:35:11,600 --> 00:35:13,200
Hyung.

383
00:35:13,570 --> 00:35:17,590
No matter how trivial, report it all to me.

384
00:35:32,830 --> 00:35:35,460
Kang Yoo Jeong is the one who...

385
00:35:35,480 --> 00:35:39,330
killed the woman Min Hyeok loved.

386
00:35:39,330 --> 00:35:42,750
Knowing that and staying by her side...

387
00:35:44,430 --> 00:35:47,530
Despicable, those two.

388
00:35:49,580 --> 00:35:52,710
I thought I knew Min Hyeok..

389
00:35:52,710 --> 00:35:55,260
But these days, I don't know anymore.

390
00:35:55,290 --> 00:35:58,070
The obsession over that woman...

391
00:35:59,270 --> 00:36:01,850
That reminds me of dead Seo Ji Hee.

392
00:36:04,320 --> 00:36:06,740
Didn't you come because you had something to say?

393
00:36:06,780 --> 00:36:08,220
Yes.

394
00:36:11,790 --> 00:36:14,470
I said before that...

395
00:36:15,540 --> 00:36:18,130
...there was a woman I loved, right?

396
00:36:21,250 --> 00:36:24,130
So the woman I wanted to be with...

397
00:36:29,100 --> 00:36:31,100
was Kang Yoo Jeong.

398
00:36:37,660 --> 00:36:38,600
Do Hoon...

399
00:36:38,600 --> 00:36:40,920
I didn't want to hear anything from other people.

400
00:36:40,950 --> 00:36:44,920
Did it not occur to you that you were pretending 
not to know that girl in front of Min Hyeok and I?!

401
00:36:45,000 --> 00:36:47,800
Jo Min Hyeok already knew.

402
00:36:51,190 --> 00:36:53,620
The three of you have, at this very moment,

403
00:36:54,290 --> 00:36:56,660
made me into a fool.

404
00:36:57,300 --> 00:36:59,260
It wasn't intended, but

405
00:36:59,280 --> 00:37:01,740
having lied to you as a result...

406
00:37:02,170 --> 00:37:04,370
made me distressed.

407
00:37:04,380 --> 00:37:05,930
I'm sorry.

408
00:37:06,660 --> 00:37:08,790
You are "sorry".

409
00:37:12,120 --> 00:37:13,510
You say it so easily.

410
00:37:13,510 --> 00:37:16,070
I didn't know it'd turn out like this.

411
00:37:16,070 --> 00:37:18,270
With Yoo Jeong, it was already over.

412
00:37:18,270 --> 00:37:22,820
I also can't [stand] the wicked things Jo Min Hyeok is doing to her...

413
00:37:23,650 --> 00:37:25,480
You're just the same.

414
00:37:26,260 --> 00:37:28,380
All men are the same.

415
00:37:29,200 --> 00:37:33,600
I was a bit strange to hope that you were different.

416
00:37:35,630 --> 00:37:37,130
Se Yeon.

417
00:37:37,140 --> 00:37:40,230
Isn't it enough that I've gone along with it while it lasted?

418
00:37:40,700 --> 00:37:43,200
Don't give your excuses.

419
00:37:43,200 --> 00:37:45,970
Since you didn't want to hear anything from anyone anyway.

420
00:38:03,490 --> 00:38:05,990
Let's drink this that I made.

421
00:38:08,400 --> 00:38:09,720
Oh~ It's hot.

422
00:38:16,970 --> 00:38:19,700
Do you remember what you said when we didn't have
any work to do,

423
00:38:19,710 --> 00:38:23,400
and we were in the room all day?

424
00:38:23,400 --> 00:38:24,600
What was that?

425
00:38:24,600 --> 00:38:28,100
If you bear it, 1 minute becomes 1 hour,

426
00:38:28,100 --> 00:38:30,770
1 hour become a month.

427
00:38:30,770 --> 00:38:34,540
Even if you don't fret, the thing that passes is time.

428
00:38:36,400 --> 00:38:40,300
That's how we talked about ourselves...

429
00:38:40,300 --> 00:38:44,100
Hey, when they say how they were in their olden days,
it's all lies.

430
00:38:44,100 --> 00:38:46,260
Those are all stories to pass time.

431
00:38:46,290 --> 00:38:48,350
Even then I

432
00:38:48,350 --> 00:38:51,420
thought about how I would live in the future.

433
00:38:53,110 --> 00:38:56,150
I thought recalling what happened in the past

434
00:38:56,180 --> 00:38:59,000
was a foolish thing.

435
00:39:00,360 --> 00:39:02,340
Thinking about my father and San...

436
00:39:02,400 --> 00:39:05,500
Hey, don't think strange thoughts.

437
00:39:05,500 --> 00:39:08,320
Wasting life living as you hate others,

438
00:39:08,320 --> 00:39:10,970
that is the most unworthy thing.

439
00:39:12,460 --> 00:39:14,790
In this world,

440
00:39:14,790 --> 00:39:20,180
there are too many people who don't get punished
even though they did wrong.

441
00:39:21,560 --> 00:39:23,620
It's strange, isn't it?

442
00:39:24,450 --> 00:39:26,640
It's unfair.

443
00:39:27,790 --> 00:39:29,300
Unni!

444
00:39:29,300 --> 00:39:32,200
Come and eat Ddeok Bokki. It's all done.
(Spicy boiled rice cake - typical, cheap Korean snack).

445
00:39:46,970 --> 00:39:51,430
So what is the real nature of your relationship with our President, huh?

446
00:39:51,960 --> 00:39:55,870
Well, it's just that, you got dumped by Do Hoon Oppa, and...

447
00:39:55,880 --> 00:39:59,050
Since it's come to this, just grab onto him.

448
00:39:59,050 --> 00:40:01,040
Hey! This bitch...

449
00:40:01,040 --> 00:40:04,400
You are really too much of a "direct narration".

450
00:40:04,400 --> 00:40:07,900
Yoo Jeong, didn't you say that President will get married soon, no?

451
00:40:09,140 --> 00:40:12,860
The woman having an affair with a married man, 
is an illegitimate existence.

452
00:40:12,860 --> 00:40:15,540
Illegitimate? 
For someone who knows the law so well,

453
00:40:15,540 --> 00:40:19,300
why did you have an affair 
with the president of your business partner?

454
00:40:19,300 --> 00:40:22,500
Hey! Nasty!

455
00:40:22,500 --> 00:40:25,730
He could live without the stars or the moon, 
but he said he couldn't live without me!

456
00:40:25,730 --> 00:40:27,840
We love each other so much, we do!

457
00:40:27,840 --> 00:40:33,210
Alright that's that. But it's not for you. 
Getting involved with a matter that's not good can't end well, understand?

458
00:40:33,210 --> 00:40:38,890
Aiyoo, why? It's not like matchmaking animals. 
Would a real marriage be done like that?

459
00:40:38,890 --> 00:40:41,380
And, the boss doesn't seem interested in that woman anyway.

460
00:40:41,380 --> 00:40:42,680
Oh, really?

461
00:40:42,680 --> 00:40:44,970
Don't worry. There's nothing like that.

462
00:40:44,970 --> 00:40:48,100
Hey, you really know how to deny things!

463
00:40:48,100 --> 00:40:50,380
Then what's the reason that you're with the Boss?

464
00:40:50,380 --> 00:40:51,820
It's because you have feelings, too.

465
00:40:51,820 --> 00:40:55,080
Hey, hey! Your mouth is the only thing alive!

466
00:40:55,080 --> 00:40:58,910
Hey, why does ddeokbokki taste like this? 
Is this ddeokbokki? Go make another one.

467
00:40:58,910 --> 00:41:00,990
Hurry, make another one.

468
00:41:00,990 --> 00:41:05,480
Just bring some sugar. 
- Sugar only?

469
00:41:11,230 --> 00:41:14,930
There was a woman who came to see Kang Yoo Jeong.

470
00:41:20,660 --> 00:41:25,020
Lee Hye Jin, she served with Kang Yoo Jeong 
at the same correctional facility.

471
00:41:25,020 --> 00:41:26,010
And?

472
00:41:26,010 --> 00:41:31,290
Kang Yoo Jeong's child, 
the person who reported his abuse is this woman.

473
00:41:31,290 --> 00:41:34,530
Three days ago, Lee Ja Young who lives together,

474
00:41:34,530 --> 00:41:38,640
went and got the CCTV footage, 
which was at a location nearby the bakery.

475
00:41:38,640 --> 00:41:40,840
Bakery? When?

476
00:41:40,840 --> 00:41:47,550
It was a CCTV for traffic control. They said they took 
the footage of the day when her dad went missing.

477
00:41:47,550 --> 00:41:51,950
The child and the father...

478
00:41:56,240 --> 00:41:59,760
Find this woman. Find her no matter what.

479
00:41:59,760 --> 00:42:03,450
Also, the CCTV, find it and bring it to me.

480
00:42:03,450 --> 00:42:05,940
Yes.

481
00:42:25,580 --> 00:42:29,200
<i>I had a woman whom I loved.</i>

482
00:42:29,230 --> 00:42:31,660
<i>That woman was Kang Yoo Jeong.</i>

483
00:42:34,890 --> 00:42:38,510
<i>What's the real reason that you're stuck
 by Min Hyeok's side?</i>

484
00:42:38,510 --> 00:42:41,770
<i>It isn't different from the reason you 
have Ahn Do Hoon by your side.</i>

485
00:42:41,770 --> 00:42:44,880
<i>I also need someone by my side.</i>

486
00:43:32,280 --> 00:43:35,730
Thinking of you as a woman who killed someone...

487
00:43:35,730 --> 00:43:40,260
As I get to know you you're more incredible.

488
00:43:40,260 --> 00:43:44,310
I heard you and Do Hoon used to date.

489
00:43:45,870 --> 00:43:50,530
What are you planning between the two men?

490
00:43:50,530 --> 00:43:53,480
I'm sorry for worrying you.

491
00:43:53,480 --> 00:43:57,430
A person who's supposed to be sorry comes into the house?

492
00:43:57,430 --> 00:43:59,640
I have something I must do.

493
00:43:59,640 --> 00:44:04,800
The debt that I have to pay back to the Boss,

494
00:44:04,800 --> 00:44:09,850
and the debt that I have to receive from Ahn Do Hoon.

495
00:44:09,850 --> 00:44:12,270
So,

496
00:44:12,270 --> 00:44:16,990
you're sorry but you'll still stick by him?

497
00:44:16,990 --> 00:44:19,070
Yes.

498
00:44:19,070 --> 00:44:21,800
Do that then.

499
00:44:21,800 --> 00:44:26,100
Because taking out a slug is not even work.

500
00:44:37,710 --> 00:44:41,900
So, you want to fold this business that is making money?

501
00:44:41,900 --> 00:44:45,560
Segwang is showing interest in the King's Restaurant.

502
00:44:45,560 --> 00:44:49,860
Out of all K-Group's affiliates,
 the one that can be liquidated for cash is

503
00:44:49,860 --> 00:44:51,270
only this place.

504
00:44:51,270 --> 00:44:56,260
This place... you want to hand it over to Segwang?

505
00:44:56,260 --> 00:44:59,370
Who is it that you're supposed to be
 working for?

506
00:44:59,370 --> 00:45:02,100
With only the growth rate we have shown,

507
00:45:02,100 --> 00:45:04,630
the investment amount that the Chairman wants,

508
00:45:04,630 --> 00:45:06,450
it won't be approved by the Board of Directors.

509
00:45:06,450 --> 00:45:11,810
Since when did I need you guys' approval?

510
00:45:11,810 --> 00:45:14,730
The number of K-Hotel shares you own

511
00:45:14,730 --> 00:45:20,020
does not surpass the number of shares 
owned by the Board and Shin Se Yeon. All decisions

512
00:45:20,020 --> 00:45:22,950
will be determined by the Board.

513
00:45:44,970 --> 00:45:47,370
How is it?

514
00:45:47,370 --> 00:45:51,870
I figured you wouldn't have the time 
to come and see the paintings, so I came to hang them up for you.

515
00:45:55,560 --> 00:45:58,940
She was audacious.

516
00:45:59,020 --> 00:46:02,770
She has something to pay back to Min Hyeok, and

517
00:46:02,770 --> 00:46:08,180
from you Do Hoon, 
she has something to receive.

518
00:46:12,870 --> 00:46:18,780
Perhaps...do you still have lingering feelings 
for that woman?

519
00:46:18,780 --> 00:46:20,960
No, I don't.

520
00:46:20,960 --> 00:46:26,330
Are you sincere about wanting to 
forget Kang Yoo Jeong?

521
00:46:26,330 --> 00:46:30,570
Yes. I've forgotten.

522
00:46:30,570 --> 00:46:32,900
Then that's fine.

523
00:46:32,900 --> 00:46:38,770
Because the past has no strength anyway.

524
00:46:38,770 --> 00:46:43,850
These two people, 
you said you could split them up, right?

525
00:46:58,430 --> 00:47:01,840
Please do it.

