559
00:49:55,530 --> 00:50:01,000
Unlike your mom, I'm not a person 
who can have an intimate relationship, don't you also know that all too well?

560
00:50:01,000 --> 00:50:02,010
Shin Se Yeon!

561
00:50:02,010 --> 00:50:03,900
Do not shout!

562
00:50:05,620 --> 00:50:08,340
Neither you nor she are in your right minds.

563
00:50:08,340 --> 00:50:12,220
